quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Allaahu On Senike O Mawnii ; sabu kattal Makko ngal gooto hattanaa, ko Kanko woni Royru…óo jeyaa…óo Makko on Muhammadu (Yo Alla juulu e makko O hisna mo), O Royri mo fittaandu e …ìanndu, tawi ko o finu…óo e nder jemma. O Itti mo ka juulirde hormorde O Na…ìi mo to juulirde Bayt al Maqdisi, nden nde Men Barkiniri ban≈ãe mun dim…óe=besnaade, e demal e galleeji Annabaa…ìe (yo …ìe his) ; fii yo o yi‚Äôu yoga e Aayeeje Amen tinndin…óe e kattal baawal=e Alla Senii…óo On. Pellet, ko Kanko Alla woni Nanoowo, ko suu…óotaako Mo nanatee, Yi‚Äôoowo, suu…óotaako Mo ko yi*atee."
  17,2,"Men Okkii Muusaa (yo o his) Tawreeta, Men Wa…ói nde fewnoore …óowa …ìi…ó…ìe Israa‚Äôiila …ìen. Men Wi‚Äôani …ìe : "Wata on jogito gaanin Am hooloraa…óo mo fawoton e mun fiyakuuji mon. Ko woni, hooloree Lam Min tun =kooloree kam miin tan"."
  17,3,"Ko onon yo geyngol …ìen …ìe Men neeminirnoo da…óugol yoolaade ka waame wonndude e Nuuhu (yo o his). Annditee on neema, yetton Alla Toowu…óo On, rewon Mo Kanko tun, …óofto…óon Mo, √±entinon Nuuhu e …óum. Pellet, kanko himo …óuu…óunoo yettugol Alla Toowu…óo On."
  17,4,"Men Humpitiino …ìi…ó…ìe Israa‚Äôiila …ìen Men anndini …ìe ka Tawreeta wonnde : "Feere alaa …ìe wa…óiray boneeji ka leydi huuwugol geddi e faaro laabi …ói…ói. ∆Åe townitoray kadi e yim…ìe …ìen too√±e e bewre, …ìe yawta keeri …óin e hoore yim…ìe …ìen"."
  17,5,"Si …ìe wa…óii bonnere aranere nden, Men wurtay e ma…ì…ìe jeyaa…ìe Amen joomiraa…ìe doole tii…óu…óe nanngal, …ìe wara …ìe, …ìe riiwa…ìe, …ìe yiiloo hakkunde galleeji ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìe bonna kala ko …ìe rewi e mun. ∆äum ko fodoore Alla non, feere alaa ko wa…óaynde."
  17,6,"Refti Men ruttitanani on -onon …ìi…ó…ìi Israa‚Äôiil …ìen- laamu ngun e polgal ngal e hoore …ìen wurtanoo…ìe e dow mo'on, tuma tuuban …óon Alla. Men ∆Åeydi on jawle mon jattanoo…óe, e …ìi…ó…ìe dahanoo…ìe, Men Wa…óti on …ìur…ìe ay…ìe mon."
  17,7,"Si on mo∆¥∆¥inii golle mon …óen -onon …ìi…ó…ìe Israa‚Äôiila …ìen- no haaniri, njo…ìdi …óum ruttanto on, Alla ko yonndinii…óo gaay e golle mon. Si on bonnii kuu…óe mon …óen, battane …óum yantay e mo‚Äôon, mo∆¥∆¥ugol kuu…óe mon nafataa Alla, bonugol majje kadi lorrataa Mo. Si bonnere …ói…óa…ìere nden wa…óii, Men wurtay e mo‚Äôon ay…ìe mon …ìen fii yo …ìe hoynu on haa …óum fee√±ira ka geece mon koyeera, e fii yo …ìe naatu kadi ka Bayt al Maqdisi …ìe yirbina nde wano …ìe naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol aranol …ìe yirbini nde, e fii yo …ìe yirbin jirbingol timmungol dowlaaji …ìe …ìe fooli din."